short_description: The CP 5005 is a farm meter box with dimensions of 400 x 600 x 200 mm. The enclosure comes complete with a triangle lock key, a wall fixing bracket and a 1mm galvanised mounting plate. This product is made from ABS material, has an IP65 rating and an IK10 impact to resistance.
